---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Kostis Dovelos">
  <section class="about-grid">
    <header class="article-header" style="padding-top: 0;">
      <h1>About</h1>
    </header>

    <article class="prose">
      <p>
        I'm a wireless systems architect and consulting engineer based in Athens, Greece. I help
        defense and telecom organizations design, implement, and deploy mission-critical wireless
        systems, from architecture definition and algorithm design down to SW/HW implementation
        and integration.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is where I write things down, sometimes with equations, sometimes without.
      </p>

      <h2>The short version</h2>
    </article>

    <ul class="timeline">
      <li>
        <span class="when">2026 - now</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Senior DSP &amp; Wireless Communications Engineer</strong>, KRUSH Labs. DSP,
          SDR development, and wireless communications engineering for next-generation UAV
          datalinks.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2026 - now</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Wireless Systems Architect</strong>, Dovelos Engineering. Independent
          consultancy helping defense and telecom organizations design, implement, and deploy
          mission-critical wireless systems.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2024 - 2026</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Senior Wireless Communications Engineer</strong>, Intracom Defense. PHY design
          of next-generation MANET radios for unmanned vehicles: waveform and modem design, MIMO,
          channel coding, link adaptation, LPD/LPI.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2022 - 2024</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Antenna Engineer</strong>, Meta Materials Inc. Metamaterial-based solutions
          for 5G mmWave coverage; evolutionary optimization of anomalous reflectors.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2021 - 2022</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Postdoctoral Research Fellow</strong>, Queen's University Belfast.
          Superdirectivity for energy-efficient mmWave/sub-THz massive MIMO (ERC project
          BEATRICE).
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2017 - 2021</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>PhD</strong>, Universitat Pompeu Fabra, Barcelona. Novel PHY concepts for 6G:
          ultra-massive MIMO, intelligent reflecting surfaces, interference alignment.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2015 - 2016</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Research Intern</strong>, CTTC, Barcelona. Implemented a slotted ALOHA
          network using LoRa radios and STM32 microcontrollers.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="when">2014 - 2015</span>
        <p class="what">
          <strong>Graduate Research Assistant</strong>, EPFL, Lausanne. Investigated the
          finite-length performance of irregular repetition slotted ALOHA (IRSA).
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Base>
